{
  "stem": "293.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 19.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somebody wanted, I got a few of those velour hats from him, and make a couple zloty or a few dollars.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then everything was permittable, except you cannot sell currency, like dollars, or German marks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was-- or- or English pound.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was not allowed by the law and was punishable by death for the Jew or for Polacks maybe to go and-- and-- to jail for a few years or maybe even to a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How, how I make my life?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I met my wife-- this is a-- she should probably told you, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was extraordinary story, because in this time I was living with my friends, not with my parents.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my friends still have the store wholesale skin-- raw skin, like for shoes, for clothes, for handbags, you understand.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were trying to unload it as much as possible of the skins so that we will not be confiscated by the Germans because they were confiscating it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Again, this way I was making certain amount of profit and making living supporting my family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father didn't make any money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother, mother still was interior decorator and still was making some money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But was very, very difficult, because we were kicked out from this apartment, I think.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So by the end of October or beginning of September, we lost everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When we received the apartment back, it was completely empty walls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nothing in it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everything disappeared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we lost almost everything in about, I would say, half an hour time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, what happened with my wife-- this is a very interesting story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One day there came an order that the Jewish family has to accept people, for-- not only Jewish, they were liquidating the intelligentsia of the city of Lodz.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
